        - Add left-out test files


0.03    2009-11-18 (SHARYANTO)

        - Fix typo in documentation


0.02    2009-11-18 (SHARYANTO)

        - Add meta_yaml_ok() and meta_spec_ok(), a la Test::CPAN::Meta


0.01    2009-11-18 (SHARYANTO)

        - First release
